{"id":232,"parent_id":224,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":232,"title":"Hebrews 8","subtitle":"","short_title":"Heb.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 8"],[".studySummary",["i","Christ offered Himself as a sacrifice for sin—God promised to make a new covenant with Israel."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.1","order":"03.21.008.23938"},["b","1"],"Now of the things which we have spoken",["i","this is"],"the sum: We have such an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"high priest"],", who is set on the right hand of the throne of the Majesty in the heavens;"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.2","order":"03.21.008.23939"},["b","2"],"A minister of the sanctuary, and of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"true"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"tabernacle"],", which the Lord pitched, and not man."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.3","order":"03.21.008.23940"},["b","3"],"For every high priest is ordained to offer gifts and sacrifices: wherefore",["i","it is"],"of necessity that this man have somewhat also to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"offer"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.4","order":"03.21.008.23941"},["b","4"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"For"],"if he were on earth, he should not be a priest, seeing that there are",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"priests"],"that offer gifts according to the law:"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.5","order":"03.21.008.23942"},["b","5"],"Who serve unto the example and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"shadow"],"of heavenly things, as Moses was admonished of God when he was about to make the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"tabernacle"],": for, See, saith he,",["i","that"],"thou make all things according to the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"pattern"],"shewed to thee in the mount."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.6","order":"03.21.008.23943"},["b","6"],"But now hath he obtained a more excellent ministry, by how much also he is the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"mediator"],"of a better",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"covenant"],", which was established upon better",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"promises"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.7","order":"03.21.008.23944"},["b","7"],"For if that first",["i","covenant"],"had been",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"faultless"],", then should no place have been sought for the second."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.8","order":"03.21.008.23945"},["b","8"],"For finding fault with them, he saith, Behold, the days come, saith the Lord, when I will make a new covenant with the house of Israel and with the house of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Judah"],":"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.9","order":"03.21.008.23946"},["b","9"],"Not according to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"covenant"],"that I made with their fathers in the day when I took them by the hand to lead them out of the land of Egypt; because they continued not in my covenant, and I regarded them not, saith the Lord."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.10","order":"03.21.008.23947"},["b","10"],"For this",["i","is"],"the covenant that I will make with the house of Israel after those days, saith the Lord; I will put my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"laws"],"into their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"mind"],", and write them in their",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"hearts"],": and I will be to them a God, and they shall be to me a people:"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.11","order":"03.21.008.23948"},["b","11"],"And they shall not teach every man his neighbour, and every man his brother, saying, Know the Lord: for all shall know me, from the least to the greatest."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.12","order":"03.21.008.23949"},["b","12"],"For I will be merciful to their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"unrighteousness"],", and their sins and their iniquities will I",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"remember"],"no more."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.13","order":"03.21.008.23950"},["b","13"],"In that he saith, A",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"new",["i","covenant"]],["i",","],"he hath made the first old. Now that which decayeth and waxeth",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"old"],["i","is"],"ready to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"vanish"],"away."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.1a","order":"03.21.008.23951"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/high-priest-melchizedek-priesthood"},"TG High Priest, Melchizedek Priesthood"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-authority-of"},"Jesus Christ, Authority of"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.2a","order":"03.21.008.23953"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.24"},"Heb. 9:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.2b","order":"03.21.008.23955"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/40.2"},"Ex. 40:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.11.11-24"},"Heb. 9:11 (11–24)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.3a","order":"03.21.008.23957"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/5.2"},"Eph. 5:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.4a","order":"03.21.008.23959"},["b","4a"],["span.small","JST"],"Heb. 8:4",["i","Therefore while he was on the"],"earth, he",["i","offered for a sacrifice his own life for the sins of the people. Now every priest under the law, must needs"],"offer gifts,",["i","or sacrifices,"],"according to the law."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.4b","order":"03.21.008.23961"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priest-aaronic-priesthood"},"TG Priest, Aaronic Priesthood"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bd/priests"},"BD Priests"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.5a","order":"03.21.008.23963"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-types-of-in-anticipation"},"TG Jesus Christ, Types of, in Anticipation"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.5b","order":"03.21.008.23965"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/35.11"},"Ex. 35:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.5c","order":"03.21.008.23967"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/7.44"},"Acts 7:44"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.6a","order":"03.21.008.23969"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-atonement-through"},"TG Jesus Christ, Atonement through"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-authority-of"},"Jesus Christ, Authority of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.6b","order":"03.21.008.23971"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/7.22"},"Heb. 7:22"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/covenants"},"TG Covenants"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-melchizedek"},"Priesthood, Melchizedek"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.6c","order":"03.21.008.23973"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/promise"},"TG Promise"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.7a","order":"03.21.008.23975"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/7.11.11-16"},"Heb. 7:11 (11–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.8a","order":"03.21.008.23977"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-judah-people-of"},"TG Israel, Judah, People of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.9a","order":"03.21.008.23979"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/law-of-moses"},"TG Law of Moses"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.10a","order":"03.21.008.23981"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-law-of"},"TG God, Law of"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.10b","order":"03.21.008.23983"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mind"},"TG Mind"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.10c","order":"03.21.008.23985"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/31.33"},"Jer. 31:33"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.3"},"2 Cor. 3:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.12a","order":"03.21.008.23987"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.14"},"D&C 38:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.12b","order":"03.21.008.23989"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/forgive"},"TG Forgive"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.13a","order":"03.21.008.23991"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.15"},"Heb. 9:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/12.47.46-47"},"3 Ne. 12:47 (46–47)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/15.3.2-10"},"15:3 (2–10)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/13.9"},"Ether 13:9"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/new-and-everlasting-covenant"},"TG New and Everlasting Covenant"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.13b","order":"03.21.008.23993"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.17"},"2 Cor. 5:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.13c","order":"03.21.008.23995"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/12.46.19,46"},"3 Ne. 12:46 (19, 46)"],"."]]}
